-- Venezuela Has No Plans to Lift Currency Controls, Chavez Says on State TV
-- Jose Orozco
-- 2010-06-17T02:22:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/venezuela-has-no-plans-to-lift-currency-controls-chavez-says-on-state-tv.html

          
          
             Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez 
said his country has no plans to lift currency controls. Chavez
spoke on state television tonight.  
